<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF109-671-021  </DOCNO><DOCID>09 671 021.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Digital Review  Dec 10 1990 v7 n48 p30(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Cahners-Ziff Publishing Associates LP 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Verdix adds Ada development series to RISC/Ultrix systems. (VerdixCorp.'s Verdix Development System)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Varney, Sarah E.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Verdix Corp. (Product enhancement).andO;Ticker:    VRDX.andO;Product:   Ada Development System (Program development software) (Productenhancement).andO;Topic:     EnhancementsADACompilersProgram Development ToolsSoftware Migration.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Verdix adds Ada development series to RISC/Ultrix systemsandM;CHANTILLY, Va.andP;  -- Verdix has announced the availability of the Verdix AdaDevelopment System (VADS) for RISC/Ultrix systems.andM;VADS provides an Ada development environment for self-hosted and embeddedsystems applications.andP;  The system provides a self-hosted Ada compiler, awindow-oriented source level debugger and access to Ada source code duringdebugging sessions.andM;VADS is already available for VMS, and is used in Ada developmentenvironments where there are complex software units to be managed thatrequire fast compilation.andP;  Ada is used almost exclusively by governmentagencies and contractors.andM;VADS is suited for large software development projects requiring 1 million to3 million lines of code, said Roger Baker, Verdix marketing director.andM;&quot;There are special problems that occur with much larger programs,&quot; Bakersaid.andP;  &quot;Linking subroutines can become a large problem due to the timerequired for linkage.andP;  With VADS, we've changed the way the linker reacts inorder to speed linkage.&quot;andM;VADS for DECstations and DECsystems will be sold by Verdix and DEC.andP;  It ispriced from $7,500 to $50,000, depending on configuration.andM;Verdix Corp. is located at Sullyfied Business Park, 14130-A SullyfieldCircle, Chantilly, VA 22021, (703) 378-7600.andO;</TEXT></DOC>